dataList.appIntro:
Bonjour!  [  Hello in French ;)  ]
The Diamond Eiffel Tower Pink Paris Keyboard Theme is a free girl theme that will make your phone keyboard fun and sparkle. Get instantly swept away to France with this Paris keyboard. The pink Paris theme wallpaper is loaded with flowers, roses and screened sayings such as "Paris," "France, "Eiffel Tower," and "Sweethearts." The beautiful teal blue diamond Eiffel Towers sits in the middles surrounded by hanging teal diamond hearts. The transparent keyboard glow and turn a light pink when tapped. The teal jeweled icons match the pink theme and sparkle on the custom wallpaper. A custom font was picked to bring this theme to life. 
If you like diamond keyboards, you’ll love this! Download the Diamond Eiffel Tower Pink Paris Keyboard Theme and escape to France while adding sparkle and diamonds to your phone. ❤
Features for Diamond Eiffel Tower Pink Paris Keyboard Theme:
★ Loaded with flowers, roses and screened sayings such as "Paris," "France, "Eiffel Tower," and "Sweethearts" creates a beautiful wallpaper for this pink keyboard
★ A teal blue diamond Eiffel Towers surrounded by hanging teal diamond hearts
★ The teal jeweled diamond heart pops up when a key is pressed
★ Custom teal jeweled icons to match
★ Custom font to match 
Keyboard features:
✪ Gesture input makes typing fast and fun with a slide of your finger
✪ Smart Prediction: Keyboard will learn your way of writing including words, phrase and favorite expressions
✪ Multilingual Typing: Supports over 120 languages
✪ Emojis: A large emoji selection to express yourself when words are just not enough
✪ Compatibility: Keyboard is compatible with most Android phone, along with many popular apps
Please read before installing. This Diamond Eiffel Tower Pink Paris Keyboard Theme requires a separate keyboard to apply. Please install and follow the simple instructions. This theme is not supported by other keyboards.
Download this app today and starting enjoying your Paris escape! Have a suggestion for a city keyboard? Feel free to email us!
Thank you for your support ❤
